TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY as FCST_SKU_KEY, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID as BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STD_COST as STD_COST, TRIM(FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STYLE_NUM) as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.COLOR_CODE) as COLOR_CODE, TRIM(FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.ATTRIBUTION_CODE) as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, TRIM(FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.SIZE_CODE) as SIZE_CODE FROM FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT WHERE SBU_PRIMARY_IND = 'Y' AND (DISC_DATE IS NULL OR DISC_DATE>=SYSDATE)
